<%= tag.div({class: 'text-center'}) do %>
  <%= tag.h1 'Welcome to my Personal Site!' %>
<% end %>
<%= tag.div do %>
  My name is Jason Colyer, and this is my website. By trade, I am a programmer and system administrator. While I know several languages, my favorites are:
  <%= tag.ul do %>
    <%= tag.li 'Ruby' %>
    <%= tag.li 'Node/Javascript' %>
    <%= tag.li 'Bash' %>
  <% end %>
  I am currently working for <%= link_to 'FlyData', 'https://www.flydata.com', {target: '_blank'} %> in a role of Support/DevOps Engineer. My background ranges from system administration to programming to pure DevOps. 
<% end %>
<%= tag.hr %>
<%= tag.div({class: 'recent-posts'}) do %>
  <%= tag.h3 'Recent Posts' %>
  <% @posts.each do |post| %>
    <%= tag.div({class: 'post-summary'}) do %>
      <%= tag.h4 do %>
        <%= link_to post.title, post_path(post.id) %>
      <% end %>
      <%= post.content[0...250] %>...
    <% end %>
  <% end %>
<% end %>
<%= tag.hr %>
